c: 34
v: 19
t: "Ndipo iwo adati, “oh Ambuye wathu! Titalikitsireni mitunda yoti tiziyendamo.” Ndipo iwo adzipondereza okha. Kotero Ife tidawasandutsa kukhala nkhaniimeneimakambidwakambidwandipotidawamwaza m’magulumagulu. Ndithudi mu chimenechi muli phunziro kwa aliyense amene amapirira ndi kuthokoza"